divs: Sighting DetailsWalked outside after cooking to cool off looked up to the sky and seen what I thought was a satellite so I called out family to look but the one became many.They looked like 40 0r 50 satellites moving overhead at the same speed of a satellite or the ISS.I called the local news and local Police Dept to see if any kind of activity was going on that night there was zero activity.So I called the local news back to touch base and see if any other reports came in.When I called the lady from the news went on our local Police dept Face Book page and seen someone had seen something the Wed before.I am still amazed at what we seen and cant explain it.This is driving me crazy because I have never seen anything like this and Im getting zero help.I just found this site and thought I should report it to someone who may care.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Memphis
